姑娘的未来倍加关心。在有关姜萍未来的消息中，这样一个说法让人们颇为唏嘘：“姜萍的梦想是浙大，但由于专业限制，她只能就读江苏省内的三所高校，最好的能申请到常熟理工学院。”于是，很多人网上喊话各高校希望他们能破格录取姜萍，尤其是姜萍心仪的浙大更是被人们反复追问。 但是，姜萍能申请的最好学校是常熟理工的说法并不准确。“中专生想上高校有两种途径，一种是专门针对中职学生的职教高考，可报考院校比较少但难度相对较低；还有一种就是参加普通高考，中职学生也是可以参加的，报考的学校基本上没有限制，关键就在于成绩怎么样，成绩够了考清华北大都是可以的。”前述江苏省教育系统内的相关人士说。 （来源：华夏时报） 教育部门称成绩够姜萍考清华北大都行_高校_高考_江苏省"},"attached_info":"CkAIh/mP9pfR1PVDEAMaCTEwODc5NDI2MiCV1cmzBjAAOMMEQApyCTY1OTMyNDA0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"77 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-26d13f52e27c02b7adc1011b5eb1992c_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1718903746.793500","card_id":"Q_659214407","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":659214407,"title":"既然《王者荣耀》的 ELO 机制饱受诟病，到底有什么好处，能让厂商宁愿得罪玩家也要继续使用呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/659214407","type":"question","created":1718672103,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":32,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,1750,163534],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ih/mP9pfR1PVDEAMaCTEwODc2OTk0MyDntcOzBjAAOCBAC3IJNjU5MjE0NDA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"77 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c8e46f45d2e58ba70913f9aab36acbec_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1718903746.793869","card_id":"Q_659421426","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":659421426,"title":"外交部表示「敦促美方撤销售台武器的错误决定，停止武装台湾」，释放了哪些信号？","url":"